<hr>
<h3><a name="desc"> Course Description</a></h3>
<p>Design and implementation of distributed object programs using
middleware software standards; interface definition languages and
programming language mappings; static and dynamic object communication
mechanisms.</p>
<p><i><font size="3">Topics:</font></i></p>
<p>1. Sockets and Socket Programming<br>
2. RMI Programming<br>
3. Distributed Object Programming</p>
<hr>
